I had no idea that former sports cabinet secretary Rashid Echesa would come to my office, neither had he booked an appointment with me on Thursday last week! Well, that is the latest statement from deputy president William Ruto, distancing himself from a multi?billion shillings military ware scandal, alleged to have been fraudulently inked at his Harambee house annex office. And as our political affairs reporter Murimi Mwangi now tells us, Ruto says all his top aides were away from annex office at the alleged time of the fraudulent annex office deal, assisting him with his official duties at his karen office